{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Copy and paste the following URL in Extensions > ReaPack > Import a Repository: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Gla1wo/AVS-Reascripts/refs/heads/master/index.xml\par}
